Glay: Groundwork Layer (C++)
============================

Overview
--------

My small utility library for C++.



Installation
------------

Currently builds only on Windows.

Grab a C++ compiler compatible with basic C++11 features such as GCC, update
the Makefile.conf if needed and run make.



